Package it.unisa.diem.softwareengineering.assignment2021

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComplexNumber
    A representation of a Complex Number that with a real part and an imaginary part.
    ComplexOperations
    Operations on Complex Numbers, developed in a Math-like style.
    GUI
    This is the principal interface class, it manage the user input and show graphically the correct output
    Manager
    The Manager of the Complex Calculator, which makes the comunication between the GUI, the Memory and the available operations possible.
    Memory
    A stack that manages complex numbers, which can be observed.
    PersonalizedOperationsMap
    A map that manages the personalized operations' representation and its persistence.
    PersonalizedOperationsWindow
    This secondary interface allow the user to interact, with the Personalised Operations
    Variables
    A treemap that manages the variables the user can use to store and load variables from, which takes alphabetical lowercase characters as keys and ComplexNumber as values.
    VariablesHandler
    A handler for the Variables class, which manages the current runtime variables and the old states of the variables when the save and restore commands are called, by keeping them in a stack.
    VariablesWindow
    This secondary interface allow the user to interact with the Auxiliary Variables
